    "Description": "A security vulnerability has been detected in Aider-AI Aider 0.86.3.dev. This affects the function requests.get of the file api_docs.py of the component AWS EC2 Metadata Endpoint. The manipulation leads to server-side request forgery. The attack is possible to be carried out remotely. The exploit has been disclosed publicly and may be used. It is suggested to install a patch to address this issue. The pull request to fix this issue awaits acceptance.",
